ge sphera offers its clients a possibility to extend their shcp services with the sphera critical diseases protection program a plan that guarantees rapid access to the best international trea tments when it is most important and all this without any extra costs and expenses cocreation of health products with combined services   tailormade programs through sphera services   health products developed to cover specific market needs local services we develop and implement best practices for governments organizations and institutions requiring marketspecific health care needs strategic planning human capital strategy efficient allocation of resources investment security and control embedded in local cultures and equipped with industryleading knowledge and perspectives on the worldwide health care market sphera strives for the best practices and networks in global medicine and spreads them out locally enhancing quality of life this is the first healthcare center opened by the sphera global health care group in luanda with the opening of cmi our clients now have access to an ambulatory center with modern facilities cuttingedge technology and a team of professional experts in the heart of luanda connected to the exclusive medical network of sphera wwwcmiluandacom adding value reducing costs sphera is a perfect addition for insurance companies looking to add value to their product lines with telemedicine and access to the international and local medicine in a controlledcost environment for insurers • concentration of international medical quality services in a single provider • internationalization of the medical services offered • product portfolio differentiation • incorporation of highly demanded services • increasing priority clients’ loyalty • improving brand perception • outsourcing of management coordination and hospital cost control services • reduction of expenses for corporations inclusion of much soughtafter social benefits capacity to extend the coverage to empl