rough sphera services health products developed to cover specific market needs international medical network as health care experts we aim to offer our members the best possible and suitable medical assistance that means having the finest hospitals and private clinics around the world the type of facilities that can offer the security and peace of mind needed at key moments in our lives clinical expertise the committee’s experience and knowhow is without doubt one of the hallmarks of our health care services model our medical officers study and analyse each case in depth drawing on their extensive knowledge of the numerous centres that make up our network they advise and guide patients to select the option best suited to their needs medical concierge staffed by a multilingual contact centre and a team of specialized health care case managers sphera assigns an advisor to each patient to coordinate and oversee the case throughout the entire process and address patient questions and concerns tech tools our knowledge of the most recent trends and best practices allows us not only to create and provide superior services but also to offer crucial assessment and information to empower patients using the most cuttingedge ehealth tools local services we develop and implement best practices for governments organizations and institutions requiring marketspecific health care needs strategic planning human capital strategy efficient allocation of resources investment security and control embedded in local cultures and equipped with industryleading knowledge and perspectives on the worldwide health care market sphera strives for the best practices and networks in global medicine and spreads them out locally enhancing quality of life this is the first healthcare center opened by the sphera global health care group in luanda with the opening of cmi our clients now have access to an ambulatory center with modern facilities cuttingedge technology and a team of professional experts in